head.title: Meetup RSVPs v2

item.comments: Ooops, I'm singing a concert that night. I look forward to the next party.
I'll be performing that evening in Stoneham. Maybe next time.
Sorry to miss it, I'll be out of town. I hope to be at the next one.
If the 30-50 group had worked out I'd be more interested in coming; need more people in my age group.
My high school reunion is Sat. PM. I won't tell you which one, but the wheel was invested in my Freshman year! LOL. See you at another dance and best of luck!
I see that the one male friend I said I was bringing, well, he joined by himself and for himself!!
There will be people from other groups there also.
Yes look forward to hanging out with a very nice group of people.
I'm not sure about bringing a friend as yet. I will try to find out asap.
Hopefully, I plan on being there !!.. Besides" I'm Italian" (lol)
